TABEL: teams

id (PK)
name
type
created_by (FK -> users.id)
created_at

TABEL: team_members

id (PK)
team_id (FK -> teams.id)
user_id (FK -> users.id)
role (optional: member/manager)
joined_at

TABEL: todos

id (PK)
title
description
created_by (FK -> users.id)
due_date (optional)
status (pending / in_progress / completed / archived)
visibility (private / team / specific_users)
team_id (nullable, FK -> teams.id)
created_at
updated_at

TABEL: todo_assignees

id (PK)
todo_id (FK -> todos.id)
user_id (FK -> users.id)

Catatan:

Private todo: tidak butuh data di todo_assignees

Team todo: bisa assign otomatis semua team members atau tidak

Specific user: simpan user yang punya akses di sini